officialTitle: To improve access to emergency medical services, and for other purposes.
shortTitle: Health Care Safety Net Enhancement Act of 2011
subjects: Emergency medical services and trauma care
summary: Health Care Safety Net Enhancement Act of 2011 - Amends the Public Health Service Act to deem a hospital or an emergency department and a physician or physician group of such hospital or emergency department to be an employee of the Public Health Service for purposes of any civil action that may arise due to providing emergency and post-stabilization services on or after January 1, 2012.
